      "content": "but i really dont think i need a hospital... i went like two months ago for these exact same feelings and they just said it was stress and my anxiety was acting up. it's just such a hassle and the waiting room is always so draining. do you think it's possible it's just the same old anxiety stuff coming back? it's been a really stressful week.",
